Class StudentView

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.cz2002.grp3.View.StudentView
All Implemented Interfaces:
UserView
public class StudentView
extends java.lang.Object
implements UserView
The Class that displays student options and receive input from the student. Relays the user input to the respective functions in studentController.
Author:
Guat Kwan, Wei Xing, Ashton, Yi Bai, Zhe Ming
